data.description: Welcome to 12780 Lincoln Way! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom brick ranch home is exactly what you've been looking for! Nestled on a corner lot in Norwin School District, there are so many benefits of this home. Just a few include an integral garage, plenty of storage space, and a low maintenance, level yard. The sunroom offers endless possibilities; a place to have your morning coffee, entertain your guests, or utilize as added living space. The spacious, updated main bathroom offers wall to wall counter space and cabinetry. The partially finished basement has so much potential to make your own. And with Route 30 minutes away, traveling is a breeze. A short drive to the park and ride and the bus will take you straight to downtown Pittsburgh. Don't miss this one!
